OL,3,CLib Dem leader says government must
OL,4,Ccover cost of cleaning up waste
OL,5,Cmountain
OL,7,FThe Leader of the Liberal Democrats,
OL,8,FSir Ed Davey, said the government must
OL,9,Finstruct the Environment Agency to
OL,10,Fclear up hundreds of tonnes of waste
OL,11,Ffound in a flip-tip in a field between
OL,12,Fthe River Cherwell and the A34 in
OL,13,FKidlington, Oxfordshire.
OL,15,FDavey said he is "totally shocked that
OL,16,Fthese criminals have been allowed to
OL,17,Fdo it in the first place and allowed
OL,18,Fto get away with it."
