OL,7,FHe told ITV News Meridian the threat
OL,8,Fto the River Cherwell is "huge" and is
OL,9,F"deeply alarmed the government,
OL,10,Fthrough the Environment Agency, is not
OL,11,Ftaking action now."
OL,13,FThe 'waste mountain' has reached 150
OL,14,Fmetres long, 10 metres wide and 12
OL,15,Fmetres high, with the Environment
OL,16,FAgency (EA) declaring it as a
OL,17,F'critical incident.'
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
