OL,7,FBut the body said "they don't have the
OL,8,Fstatutory duty" to clear up the waste
OL,9,F- the criminals should be footing the
OL,10,Fbill.
OL,12,FDavey stated "when I questioned the
OL,13,FPrime Minister, he admitted it was the
OL,14,FEA's role but they are waiting until
OL,15,Fthey catch the people who did this,
OL,16,Fbefore they clean it up.
OL,18,F"That is nonsense. The threat to land,
OL,19,Fto the water, to the environment -
OL,20,Fthey need to act now."
