OL,7,FThe Environment Agency first visited
OL,8,Fthe site at the beginning of July,
OL,9,Fafter it was reported to the
OL,10,Forganisation, finding significant
OL,11,Famounts of waste and issuing a cease
OL,12,Fand desist letter to stop further
OL,13,Ftipping.
OL,15,FWhen more waste dumping was reported
OL,16,Fin October, the agency applied for and
OL,17,Fsecured a court order to close down
OL,18,Fthe site, and is now taking action to
OL,19,Fprevent pollution from the waste pile
OL,20,Fand investigate the illegal activity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
