OL,7,FThe MP for Bicester & Woodstock, Calum
OL,8,FMiler, had previously suggested it'll
OL,9,Fcost #25m to deal with the incident,
OL,10,Fwhich would exceed the entire yearly
OL,11,Fbudget for Cherwell District Council.
OL,13,F"The scale of what we see behind us is
OL,14,Fso large that it requires government
OL,15,Faction," Miller said. "This is the
OL,16,FEA's responsibility, but they haven't
OL,17,Fput enough resource behind it.
OL,19,F"What we urgently need is Secretary of
OL,20,FState for the Environment to instruct
OL,21,Fthe EA and clear up the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
