OL,7,F"This is criminal
OL,8,Factivity...ultimately they must be
OL,9,Fmade to pay for that. We cannot wait
OL,10,Ffor that money to be recouped from the
OL,11,Fcriminals, so in the short term, the
OL,12,Fnational government should step in -
OL,13,Fas they did in Kent last year - and
OL,14,Finstruct EA to take action."
OL,16,FIt's been described as an
OL,17,Fenvironmental catastrophe by local
OL,18,Fcampaigners, who fear chemicals from
OL,19,Fthe rubbish will harm wildlife and
OL,20,Fpotentially run into the River
OL,21,FCherwell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
