OL,5,Cmountain
OL,7,FThe Environment Secretary, Emma
OL,8,FReynolds, said: "I've instructed the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency to take decisive
OL,10,Faction to reduce the risk of
OL,11,Fenvironmental harm and I am pleased
OL,12,Fthey are now installing additional
OL,13,Fbarriers to prevent pollution of the
OL,14,FCherwell.
OL,16,F"I am being regularly updated on the
OL,17,Fongoing investigation, and I want to
OL,18,Fsee justice served for this disgusting
OL,19,Fcrime."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
