OL,7,FThe CEO of the Environment Agency,
OL,8,FPhilip Duffy, said he shared the local
OL,9,Fcommunity's "disgust at this case of
OL,10,Fenvironmental vandalism" and they have
OL,11,Finstalled protective barriers at the
OL,12,Fsite.
OL,14,F"In the event of heavy rainfall, they
OL,15,Fwill help minimise the risk of waste
OL,16,Fmoving into the nearby River Cherwell
OL,17,Fand thereby protect its water quality."
